{"tid":2151910,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"輪椅漢買不到《蘋果》 聲援屯門和你Sing 希望黎智英大步檻過","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T23:46:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2f8b803a6d02b3c5ca50a3edc0f4c7a210abf7","tid":2151910,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200811/BLYNTBES264KXHWSHNAQYVORA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200811%2FBLYNTBES264KXHWSHNAQYVORA4%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=aa57f04c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200811%2FBLYNTBES264KXHWSHNAQYVORA4%2F&h=065afc1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200811/BLYNTBES264KXHWSHNAQYVORA4/</a><br />\n<br />\n網民發起「和你Sing」活動捍衞新聞自由，晚上除了沙田新城巿廣場有巿民聲援之外，屯門巿廣場晚上約亦有30名市民參與，66歲的輪椅使用者徐先生是其中之一。他表示自己是《蘋果日報》的忠實讀者，惟今日下午去過幾間便利店都買不到《蘋果日報》，之後得知屯門市廣場有「和你Sing」活動決定前來參與以示支持，並指希望黎智英先生可以「大步檻過」。"},{"pid":"2a0bfbc541954ac2366b9919227aad055178ffd3","tid":2151910,"uid":362346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5fe0576aa72e22eb5b6773888a10df35b9c2a0","tid":2151910,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfd765808beadc8164b21aa095f7696693d4242","tid":2151910,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a0bfbc541954ac2366b9919227aad055178ffd3","tid":2151910,"uid":362346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/l